android_install_step_one:
1. Vula isiphequluli somakhalekhukhwini wakho
  2. Ngena ku  bit.ly/concompass
  3. Cofa ibhena ethi- "Faka i-Constitution Compass kwisikrini sakho sasekhaya" ulalendele imiyalelo.
android_install_step_two:
Uma ibhena ingaveli, cofa uphawu lwe-Toolbar 
ekhoneni langesokudla phezulu. bese ucofa- "Faka i-App".
android_install_step_three: Uma ufuna ukuvula i-app, yithole kwisikrini sakho sasekhaya
cases_feature_text: Shesha uphequlule inguqulo ebuyekeziwe futhi yahlanganiswa yeMithetho yesiGungu sikaZwelonke sePhalamende.
guides_feature_text: Izinkombandlela zencazelo nenhloso yesigaba ngasinye Zomqulu Wamalungelo kanye nezahlukulo zoMthethosisekelo ezivame ukusetshenziswa.
if_no_safari_instruction:
• Vula isiphequluli sakho sakwa-Safari
    Qaphela: kufanele kube ngeyakwa-Safari, awukwazi ukusebenzisa eyakwa-Google Chrome noma eyakwa-Fiirefox.
  • Ngena ku  bit.ly/concompass
ios_install_text:
• Pheqa wehle ucofe "Faka kwisikrini sasekhaya" bese ucofa."Faka"
  • Uma ufuna ukuvula i-app, uzoyithola kwisikrini sakho sasekhaya
main_content:
Constitution Compass

i-App yoMthethosisekelo yamaLunga ePhalamende.

Phequlula, uphenye futhi uqondisise uMthethosisekelo waseNingizimu Afrika nokuthi isebenza kanjani ezimpilweni sethu sonke. Umqulu woMthethosisekelo kanye nemithetho yesiGungu sikaZwelonke sePhalamende oqoqiwe ngokunonophela futhi wabuyekezwa njalo  Rules of the National Assembly .
rules_feature_text: Izinkombandlela ezifundekayo zezihumusho zoMthethosisekelo ezikhishwa yiNkantolo yoMthomthethosisekelo yaseNingizimu Afrika.
search_feature_text: Thola ulwazi oludingayo ngokusesha uMthethosisekelo, Amazala, Izinkombandlela kanye nemiThetho yePhalamende.
